channel.title: [Delta] Teleports [Delta]
channel.description:
Hey Moparscape .....again
Well I have another problem that is leaving me at a standstill. I was setting teleports that looked something like this: http://prntscr.com/iylc1
Thing is, see where it says more? Well I copied that whole part from my Monsters teleport and added bosses. Now when I click more it works the way I want it to, but if I go to monsters, and click the one that should say more (which I changed), it brings me to the more bosses part. I was wondering how I could fix this, or if it was possible(if so how) to change the case of one of the teleports. You see, the cases for both of the last options are the same, (9194) so my code looks like this: http://prntscr.com/iylo7
